<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/680369-why-do-these-characters-speak-as-if-with-a">Why do these characters speak as if with a southern accent, but the story takes place in the north?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_680369'><a id="like_count_community_question_680369" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/680369?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18240248-i-shall-be-near-to-you">like</a></span>

