</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/51880583-lacey">Lacey</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I believe because they come from a poor, rural area. I don&apos;t think it&apos;s so much a Southern accent as a lower-class accent.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I believe because they come from a poor, rural area. I don't think it's so much a Southern accent as a lower-class accent.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
